---
import Footer from "../komponenter/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../komponenter/Header.astro";
import Bottom from "../komponenter/Bottom.astro";
import "../style/style.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Astro</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <div class="forside_wine">
      <img src="/img/forside_wine.avif" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="forside_intro">
      <h1>Welcome to,</h1>
      <h2>Bunchs WINEBAR - an artsy oasis</h2>
      <p>located in the heart of Frederiksberg.</p>
    </div>
    <Bottom />

    <img src="pic_trulli.jpg" alt="Forside billede" />

    <div id="forside_intro_2">
      <h1>We are an,</h1>
      <h2>. . . art-inspired wine bar with good, honest organic/biodynamic wine at great prices in cozy surroundings.</h2>
      <p>
        Bunch's Wine Bar is located at H.C Ørsteds Vej 50A, st. 4. in Frederiksberg. You can keep up with events on Instagram and Facebook. <br />
        <br />
         In our wine bar, we offer wine tastings for both private individuals and corporate clients, and we have a wide selection of natural wines. Therefore, you'll be able to taste wines that you can't find anywhere else. <br />
        <br />We have 12 different wines by the glass (bubbles, red, white & orange) - also full bottles. <br /> If you feel like having a little bite to eat with us, we have several different small dishes on the menu, including anchovies, burrata, pâté, serrano ham, and more.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Bottom />

    <div class="forside_illustrationer">
      <img src="/img/forside_illustrationer.webp" alt="" />
    </div>

    <img src="pic_trulli.jpg" alt="Forside billede" />

    <div id="forside_intro_2">
      <h1>Stop by,</h1>
      <h2>. . . and enjoy a good glass of natural wine.</h2>
      <p>
        Whether you're looking to savor a fine glass of wine before your meal or eager to sample a variety of wines with a group of family members, friends, or colleagues, our wine bar is definitely worth a visit. <br />
        <br />
         Here, you can indulge in our exclusive selection of natural wines, unavailable elsewhere, which go beyond just conventional wines. <br />
      </p>
    </div>

    <img src="pic_trulli.jpg" alt="Forside billede" />

    <div id="forside_intro_2">
      <h1>Moreover,</h1>
      <p>
        we regularly hold wine tastings and other events in the wine bar with plenty of entertainment, such as readings, live music, and more. <br />
        <br />

         You can keep up with upcoming events on our website or Instagram and Facebook.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Bottom />
    <div class="lys_illustration">
      <img src="/img/lys_illustration.avif" alt="" />
    </div>

    <div class="sociale_medier">
      <h1>Follow us on social media!</h1>
      <div class="sociale_medier_icon">
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61551368044436">
          <img src="/img/facebook_icon_2.avif" alt="Facebook" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bunchs.vinbar/">
          <img src="/img/instagram_icon_2.avif" alt="Instagram" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  /* Mobil styling */
  .forside_wine img {
    max-width: 80%;
    height: auto;
    margin-top: 50px;
    margin-left: 80px;
  }
  .forside_intro {
    line-height: 0.8;
    margin-left: 10px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  #forside_intro_2 {
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-left: 10px;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  .forside_illustrationer {
    margin-left: 20px;
  }
  .lys_illustration img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin-left: 270px;
  }

  .sociale_medier_icon {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .sociale_medier_icon img {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .sociale_medier_icon a img {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .sociale_medier_icon a img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.3);
  }

  /* Tablet og desktop styling */
  @media only screen and (min-width: 800px) {
  }
</style>
